   CIR-COMPUTER-COLUMN (Undated) _ The weekly column: Techniques
for back up. By Peter H. Lewis.
</P>
<P>
   CIR-BRITAIN-ROYALS (Undated) _ Want to peek at a family Web site
crammed with murder, treachery, blood-lust, centuries-long feuds,
torture, insanity and whole dungeonfuls of assorted other
skeletons? The British monarchy is just the ticket
(www.royal.gov.uk). By Michael Pollak.
